<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Offline — Tracker</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/site.css" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f6f7f9;
            margin: 0;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
            max-width: 480px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 .5rem;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="card">
        <h1> You’re offline</h1>
        <p>
            Some features aren’t available without internet. Try again when you’re
            back online.
        </p>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
